<p>There's a LOT of information on the internet and sometimes it's hard to know who you can trust. In my view, a lot of it comes down to the motivation of the writer. Good motivations generally lead to good information. So here are the 6 different types of financial bloggers that I've come across, and the main motivation that drives each.
